- Manual: explicitly dropping one or more partitions based upon its age
- Retention Policy: On a per table basis

REFERENCES:
    https://docs.timescale.com/api/latest/hypertable/drop_chunks/
    https://docs.timescale.com/api/latest/data-retention/add_retention_policy/

